%H A038147 Björg N. Cyvin, Jon Brunvoll, and Sven J. Cyvin, <a href="https://doi.org/10.1007/BFb0018563">Enumeration of benzenoid systems and other polyhexes</a>, Advances in the Theory of Benzenoid Hydrocarbons II, Springer, 1992. See Table 9 on p. 86.
%H A038147 J. V. Knop, K. Szymanski, Ž. Jeričević, and N. Trinajstić, <a href="http://match.pmf.kg.ac.rs/electronic_versions/Match16/match16_119-134.pdf">On the total number of polyhexes</a>, Match, No. 16 (1984), 119-134. See Table 7.
